Carol Vorderman, 62, showed off her gym-sculpted physique over the weekend as she shared her workout with her Instagram followers. The presenter wore skintight leather-look leggings with a long-sleeved beige top to lift weights at the gym. In the caption, Carol said she hasn't "done a proper gym sesh for a few months" but that her new personal trainer will be "stuck with her". Plenty of her fans took to the comments to gush about her impressive figure. Dan praised: "Looking good, an inspiration." And Alex encouraged: "Wow great job babe keep up the good work."